<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="50">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$gu-nian-zhi-10" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/gu-nian-zhi-10" class="zg-link" title="顾念之">顾念之</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lei-ling-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lei-ling-95" class="zg-link" title="雷零">雷零</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$henry-li-66" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/henry-li-66" class="zg-link" title="Henry Li">Henry Li</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="111073" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">多数情况下只是一个聊天的开头。因为看电视本不是交互性活动，年轻人看其他节目家长基本是插不上话的，只有英语节目可以用这个万能语句介入。<br><br>另外，当下英语仍是绝对的显学。相对其他学科，家长对子女英语水平的关注程度高也是可以理解，其实这个问题也包含着父母对子女“能听懂纯英文节目”的期望。<br><br>我一般是这样回答的：<br><br>“China's biggest e-commerce firm Alibaba Group Holding says it expects to price its initial public offering (IPO) at between $60 and $66 per a share......”<br><br>父／母：“你能不能听懂？”<br><br>我：“这是法语。”<br><br>既化解了我其实听不懂的尴尬，又显得我好像涉猎多国外语，深藏功与名。


</div>

</div>
